17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3231, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 3231. A. This act shall be known and may be cited as
20 the "Oklahoma National Guard Educational Assistance Act".
21 B. As used in this act:
22 1. "Oklahoma educational institution" means an institution of
23 higher education within The Oklahoma State System of Higher
24 Education;
